"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## New Here?\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_a3VDhXMm9HcBgzKqNvPQ.png?height=324&width=1286)\\n\\nThe **Mundo Lingo Local Embassy** is where ‚Äú[IRL](https://www.howtogeek.com/449518/what-does-irl-mean-and-how-do-you-use-it/)‚Äù [Collaborators](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/onyNgQAi-2VKGNTDGYK9vf20AK-k7i-3qot58G4Qo54) in your city hang out. Here you‚Äôll find local event managers, Ambassadors, Photographers, language school staff, venue managers and perhaps the occasional avid event fan.\\n\\n## Apply\\n\\nThe **Local Embassy** is an invite-only group. You should first join [Mundo Lingo Collaborators](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/onyNgQAi-2VKGNTDGYK9vf20AK-k7i-3qot58G4Qo54) and then apply for a local role, or let group members know you wish to contribute\\n\\n## üëã Introduce yourself\\n\\nThis is a **must**. Be noticed - Light up the sky üåü, don‚Äôt let anyone not-notice you arrived ‚ú®\\n\\n* Who are you?\\n* Are you an Admin for Telegram, Facebook or both?\\n* What are your passions, hobbies, interests?\\n* Why are you here?\\n* Who are you interested in connecting with?\\n\\n## Help Mundo Lingo in your city\\n\\n### Be Responsive\\n\\nManagers ask in here for help from Ambassadors and Photographers. If you can attend their event and help, let them know right away\\n\\n### Be Online\\n\\nJoin the Telegram room for your country. You can find a [full list here](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/N2dwMM22W_E_f68Y2mpejQKZnYRVV9m-4x3_YrF1h0M).\\n\\n### Collaborate\\n\\nConsider Collaborating by promoting your Local Embassy through social media. To join a social media task group, ask in the [Collaborators](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/onyNgQAi-2VKGNTDGYK9vf20AK-k7i-3qot58G4Qo54) room.\\n\\n### Be Supportive.\\n\\nRaise your presence in the group by acknowledging others.\\n\\n1. Give new members a **warm welcome**. Give them with your personal intro.\\n2. Have a go at answering peoples questions\\n3. Even if you don‚Äôt have an answer, let them know *‚Äòhey that‚Äôs a great question‚Äô!*\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DMfN9YsDh1DoNf19Iy_AX.png?height=677&width=1470)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1639374634,\"title\":\"Local Embassy\"},\"digest\":\"GUZj246f3hBt927EWv_XtirgExr-3Xm97nI8nak8BY0\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"I05aY3hplNIe6fTONYLYUeJY4B92IxceZCzVPtMIjWS0zaq5ptsTvnyxTR0b4OfOyDLIQVWI_rnNWtBQ81to4A\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x57d0f7cbea22222afabed23e09ac819f759269ea4cca2a83cdd992ddf3ffe88d22a7afd325b70c3c1ae7dee6f5fc8e22188ba69c589cf1f0528e258261121ae51b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"GUZj246f3hBt927EWv_XtirgExr-3Xm97nI8nak8BY0\"}"